v0.4.0 - 15 Mar 2017
------------------------
    - Switch to -drive, support for ide,scsi,virtio disk interfaces.
    - Add serial redirect to TTY and socket.
    - Add -kernel and -append features.
    - Start VM in temporary mode (-snapshot)
    - Set host IPv4 for VM tap interfaces.
    - Switch license to BSD-2-Clause.

    ! Old database is not supported, must create new, but
    ! if upgraded from >= v0.2.* then run ./upgrade_db.sh script.

v0.3.0 - 04 Mar 2017
------------------------
    - Show QEMU PID in guest info window.
    - Form navigation improvments.
    - Add mouse override feature.
    - More symbols accepted for VM names.
    - Zero tap interfaces can be configured now.
    - Fix crashes with gcc-4.9.*
    - Other bug fixes.

    ! Old database is not supported, must create new, but
    ! if upgraded from v0.2.* then run ./upgrade_db.sh script.

v0.2.1 - 25 Feb 2017
------------------------
    - Fix integer overflow on x86_32.
    - Generate user config file.

v0.2.0 - 24 Feb 2017
------------------------
    - Tab completion for file system paths.
    - BIOS file settings.
    - Install guest from disk image.
    - No root required.
    - USB device selection fixed.
    - Handle window size change for main and guests windows.
    - Config file was restructured.
    ! Old database is not supported, must create new !

v0.1.8 - 13 January 2015
------------------------
    - Code refactoring

v0.1.7 - 29 December 2014
-------------------------
    - Boot settings edit menu

v0.1.6 - 09 September 2014
--------------------------
    - Enable/Disable host CPU
    - Realtime VM window refresh
    - Bug fixes
    ! Old database is not supported, must create new !

v0.1.5 - 10 June 2014
----------------------
    - Add flag "-cpu host" if kvm is enabled

v0.1.4 - 21 April 2014
----------------------
    - Add ability to edit interface mac address and driver

v0.1.3 - 18 April 2014
----------------------
    - Variuos network drivers support
    - Fix bugs

v0.1.2 - 15 April 2014
----------------------
    - Add virtual disk to guest feature
    - Show real vnc port
    - Fix bugs

v0.1.1 - 11 April 2014
----------------------
    - Fix vnc connect bug
    - Centered view
    - Add ability to bind vnc to any interfaces or only to localhost

v0.1.0 - 10 April 2014
----------------------
    - First beta
